### Store Locations API Tests for Google Maps Integration

### Get all store locations
GET {{host}}/api/storelocations
Accept: application/json

### Get all store locations with user location (for distance calculation)
GET {{host}}/api/storelocations?userLatitude=10.8231&userLongitude=106.6297
Accept: application/json

### Get specific store location by ID
GET {{host}}/api/storelocations/1
Accept: application/json

### Get nearest store location (query params)
GET {{host}}/api/storelocations/nearest?userLatitude=10.8231&userLongitude=106.6297
Accept: application/json

### Get nearest store locations (POST with detailed request)
POST {{host}}/api/storelocations/nearest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userLatitude": 10.8231,
  "userLongitude": 106.6297,
  "limit": 5,
  "maxDistanceKm": 20
}

### Create a new store location (Ho Chi Minh City - District 1)
POST {{host}}/api/storelocations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 10.8231,
  "longitude": 106.6297,
  "address": "123 Nguyen Hue Boulevard, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam"
}

### Create another store location (Ho Chi Minh City - District 7)
POST {{host}}/api/storelocations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 10.7379,
  "longitude": 106.7218,
  "address": "456 Nguyen Thi Thap, District 7, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam"
}

### Create store location (Hanoi)
POST {{host}}/api/storelocations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 21.0285,
  "longitude": 105.8542,
  "address": "789 Hoan Kiem Lake, Hanoi, Vietnam"
}

### Update store location
PUT {{host}}/api/storelocations/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "123 Updated Address, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam"
}

### Get directions URL for Google Maps
GET {{host}}/api/storelocations/1/directions?userLatitude=10.8200&userLongitude=106.6300
Accept: application/json

### Delete store location
DELETE {{host}}/api/storelocations/1

